<br>
SCF1 = +2% = 2 AA<br>
SCF2 = +2% = 4 AA<br>
SCF3 = +3% = 6 AA<br>
FoM1 = +2% = 3 AA<br>
FoM2 = +2% = 6 AA<br>
FoM3 = +3% = 9 AA<br>
====================<br>
Total = 14% = 30 AA<br>
<br>
I don't think criticals go down with PoP. Maybe you're just unlucky. Remember even with FoM3, it's still a very small chance to critical. But while hunting in PoD, I've critical about 3-4 times with FoT in about 15 cast. Maybe I'm just lucky.<br>
